org.quickstart.api.message

Interface Message<A,M>

  • Type Parameters:
    M - defines the type of message
    A - defines the type of ActionEvent
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public interface Message<A,M>
extends java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents an message used by specific listener. An message targets a component and contains a message body; every target get a specific instance of an message (clone) containing only his specific message body and message event.
    Author:
    Andy Moncsek
